ckquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今日仲係咁撚食電呀。。痴L線 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時我懷疑係Google Play Service之類update咗，搞衰一D嘢令到部機Doze唔到，我部V10都間中係咁。你試下較Location去Battery Saving？"},{"pid":"7d357a45535486c36a1268b4b9d1299edbf2149e","tid":436043,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人部Nokia 6近呢幾日突然食電到痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今日仲係咁撚食電呀。。痴L線 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時我懷疑係Google Play Service之類update咗，搞衰一D嘢令到部機Doze唔到，我部V10都間中係咁。你試下較Location去Battery Saving？</blockquote><br />\n請問點較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我連呢部機本身有無kill apps或唔比d apps自行啟動既功能都搵唔到黎set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果無，請問有冇好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n部機係咁彈d通知出黎"},{"pid":"d5dedc87955f3f86470fdd39cea06c0dcff6834f","tid":436043,"uid":147145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其他地區唔知<br />\n但香港旗艦行低價策略頂死華碩 算幾成功<br />\n但6用430 買唔落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇人用6個touch screen開始時不時發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇，但自動旋轉太敏感"}]}